# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# English Dialogue Learner — Environment Variables
# Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your values.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# OpenAI API key (optional but strongly recommended for high-quality TTS).
# When set, the app uses OpenAI's "tts-1" model (voices: nova, shimmer, onyx, echo).
# When NOT set, the app automatically falls back to the browser's Web Speech API.
# Get a key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...your-openai-key-here...
